    <title>Signature of org.aspectj.lang</title>
    <url>/2021/12/30/spring-aop-signature/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>在学习Spring——AOP环绕通知的时候，org.aspectj.lang下有一个Signature接口，签名对象。没懂什么意思，Google了一下，解释如下：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>In <a href="https://www.thoughtco.com/what-is-java-2034117">Java</a>, a method signature is part of the method declaration. It’s the combination of the method name and the <a href="https://www.thoughtco.com/parameter-2034268">parameter</a> list.</p>
<p>The reason for the emphasis on just the method name and parameter list is because of <a href="https://www.thoughtco.com/overloading-2034261">overloading</a>. It’s the ability to write methods that have the same name but accept different parameters. The Java compiler is able to discern the difference between the methods through their method signatures.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>即此处的Signature就是方法名和参数列表的集合。</p>
<p>参考链接：<a href="https://www.thoughtco.com/method-signature-2034235">Definition of a Java Method Signature</a></p>
]]></content>
